---
import { ArrowBigDown } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-6 sm:p-12 xl:p-0 min-h-full overflow-hidden bg-[url(../assets/bg.png)] bg-no-repeat bg-cover bg-center xl:bg-top-left z-0"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black animate-fade-out"></div>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-8 justify-center items-center text-center animate-slide-in-from-bottom"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-[72px] leading-[1.1] lg:text-[96px] lg:leading-[1.1] mt-10 xl:mt-0 font-extrabold font-accent text-shadow-2xs"
    >
      Pela Web <br />
      <strong
        class="bg-linear-to-r from-indigo-500 via-violet-500 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >mais rápida</strong
      >
    </h1>
    <div>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 max-w-full sm:max-w-150 sm:text-lg">
        Com foco em agilidade e segurança, entrego interfaces robustas, fluidas
        e sem erros. Crio soluções centradas no usuário e prontas para o
        crescimento do seu negócio.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="px-5 py-3 mt-6 inline-block border-2 border-white rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors"
        >Agendar Conversa</a
      >
    </div>
    <ArrowBigDown class="animate-bounce mt-6 sm:mt-10" />
  </div>
</section>
